lable from: URL: https://cima.aemps.es/cima/publico/home.html." ([2018]):[8] "Product Information. Ifex (ifosfamide)." Bristol-Myers Squibb, Princeton, NJ.[9] "Product Information. Zanosar (streptozocin)." Pharmacia and Upjohn, Kalamazoo, MI.', 1767365204);
